Title: An Act Changing the Name of 10Th Avenue (East and West) in the City of Caloocan, Metropolitan Manila, to Daang Macario B. Asistio, Sr.
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 686
An Act Changing the Name of 10Th Avenue (East and West) in the City of Caloocan, Metropolitan Manila, to Daang Macario B. Asistio, Sr.
Section 1. The name of 10th Avenue (East and West) in the City of Caloocan, Metropolitan Manila, is changed to Daang Macario B. Asistio, Sr.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
